    "text": "Kimi 2.6 Thinking seems very good for an open weights model, but many rough edges compared to closed SoTA.\n\nThe Lem Test resulted in a 74 page thinking trace... and an okay-ish answer.\n\nIt did an okay TiKZ unicorn, an adequate twigl shader for a neogothic city in the waves, etc. https://t.co/aO14euf0Dw",
